{
  "texts": [
    "Providing an easy-to-use mechanism for the user to write a plugin to parse the logs of custom devices can be very useful for the organization.",
    "Organizations may grow in size with the passage of time and gradually add more sensors and devices.",
    "This feature considers the ability of a SIEM system to support the growing number of devices and events collected at the edge of the IT infrastructure.",
    "Vulnerabilities on the networked systems can be exploited by attackers and may lead to information theft.",
    "Vulnerabilities may arise due to a number of reasons such as misconfiguration and deployments dependencies, etc."
  ]
}